American National Adult Reading Test

Source: R/data.R
AMNART.Rd

American National Adult Reading Test data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(AMNART)

Format

A data frame with 1059 observations and 68 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI3, ADNI4, ADNI2, ADNIGO, ADNI1

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 21, ..., 10898

  • VISCODE character Visit code , with options: 4_init, 4_bl, 4_m12

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • DONE character Was assessment/procedure done? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • NDREASON character If No, reason not done 1=Participant Unable for Cognitive Reasons ; 10=Not called for by protocol ; 11=Participant in a non-USA Site ; 12=Not an English-speaking participant ; 2=Participant Unable for Other Reasons (Physical, auditory, etc.) ; 3=Participant/Study Partner Refused ; 7=Site Error ; 8=Other Reason ; 9=Unknown Decoded Value: Yes

  • EXAMDATE Examination Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SOURCE character Information Source 1=Participant Visit ; 2=Telephone Call/Video Call Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMNART1 character 1. ache 1=Correct ; 2=Incorrect Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMNART2 character 2. debt 1=Correct ; 2=Incorrect Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMNART3 character 3. pint 1=Correct ; 2=Incorrect Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMNART4 character 4. depot 1=Correct ; 2=Incorrect Decoded Value: Yes

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 95, ..., 120499

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 2, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • HAS_QC_ERROR character Has Quality Check Error 0=Does not have QC error or QC error has been approved ; 1=Has QC error Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
